{
  "stem": "4963.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, well, anyhow that's just an incident as far as the book is concerned.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I-- you know, I got my beating and I realized that I shouldn't do it again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My aunt.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't-- it wasn't very-- wasn't a bad beating, but I was really, from then on, I was really watched over, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I realized that I shouldn't-- you know, I-- I have to be-- if I'm going to do it, I have to be more secretive.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, anyhow, we had-- life in the ghetto, as I remember, as I mentioned to you, was really a challenge for me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I approached it in a way, I guess, maybe it was a child's way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember the-- the-- the children, especially the old people when they evacuated when they partitioned off the old people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were train cars.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they kept-- they-- cattle trains, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they dragged these people into them and the screamings and the yellings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I could see it, and I guess it was the-- the railroad did not go very far from-- I mean, the-- the-- the tracks were not far or was actually in the ghetto as well.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they'd bring those cars in and they were cattle-- I remember that they were little had little windows, and they would just push these people in and then there was screaming and-- and crying.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I remember the faces on the Lithuanians and the Germans as even-- cold, real straight faces with as a matter of fact and even saying, OK, hurry up.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and even beating them or shooting them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember some-- if people rebelled, they would-- I--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
